00:20:30.530 --> 00:20:35.290
Don't tell me you have a crush on me.

00:20:35.630 --> 00:20:36.940
N-No...

00:20:37.760 --> 00:20:38.560
No way!

00:20:38.560 --> 00:20:41.440
Give me a break, Senpai!

00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:43.300
N-No, I...

00:20:43.700 --> 00:20:46.710
A-All that stuff about having a crush on...

00:20:46.710 --> 00:20:48.320
On?

00:20:48.320 --> 00:20:49.680
...you aside...

00:20:51.570 --> 00:20:53.180
...aside?

00:20:54.420 --> 00:21:00.600
Honestly, you tick me off
and get on my nerves.

00:21:00.600 --> 00:21:06.230
But I don't... I don't hate it that much.

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:11.760
Talking with you and stuff, miss.

00:21:12.670 --> 00:21:15.830
Seriously, that "miss" thing is creepy.

00:21:16.060 --> 00:21:18.840
F-Fine then... your name.

00:21:19.220 --> 00:21:22.010
Tell me your n-name.

00:21:26.260 --> 00:21:27.240
Sure.

00:21:28.740 --> 00:21:31.700
"Naga" as in "long," and "toro."

00:21:31.700 --> 00:21:32.510
"Toro"?

00:21:37.260 --> 00:21:39.090
You write it like this.

00:21:39.090 --> 00:21:44.060
Toro.

00:21:48.210 --> 00:21:50.220
Call me Nagatoro from now on.

00:21:50.720 --> 00:21:53.870
Let's get to know each other, Senpai.

00:23:26.540 --> 00:23:28.320
Reflections for today!

00:23:28.320 --> 00:23:29.800
Wh-What is that supposed to mean?

00:23:29.800 --> 00:23:32.030
Senpai, you looked at my bra.

00:23:32.030 --> 00:23:33.260
I d-didn't!

00:23:33.260 --> 00:23:34.680
Lies!

00:23:34.680 --> 00:23:35.520
What color was it?

00:23:35.520 --> 00:23:37.180
I d-didn't see it!

00:23:37.180 --> 00:23:38.430
It looks like this. See?
